				<p><span class="bodytext">Clifton Public Schools is committed to providing information and education regarding the health and
well-being of our community. Recent media coverage is currently giving significant attention to COVID-19 (Coronavirus). The Clifton Public School district is implementing  precautionary measures while simultaneously
ensuring that we stay abreast of the information coming from the New Jersey Department of Education,
New Jersey Department of Health, and the Center for Disease Control.	Correspondence sent to families from Clifton Public Schools and important links are listed on this page as a reference.</span></p>
